      • unitsLeft

        public int unitsLeft()
        Implements MobilePhoneContract.entities.MobilePhoneContract.unitsLeft.
        The units left are calculated using the used units and the number of included units, more precisely, the "units left " = "included units" - "used units". The smallest possible result is zero (0).
        Specified by:
        unitsLeft in class MobilePhoneContract
        Returns:

      • additionalFee

        public float additionalFee()
        Implements MobilePhoneContract.entities.MobilePhoneContract.additionalFee.
        If there are units left, then the additional fees are 0.0. Otherwise for every used unit above the included units 0.20 EUR should be charged as additional fee.
        Specified by:
        additionalFee in class MobilePhoneContract
